quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  26,111,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ṣé kí á gbà ọ́ gbọ́ nígbà tí ó jẹ́ pé àwọn ènìyàn yẹpẹrẹ l’ó ń tẹ̀lé ọ!?”"
  26,112,"Ó sọ pé: “Èmi kò nímọ̀ sí ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe (lẹ́yìn mi)"
  26,113,"Kò sí ìṣírò-iṣẹ́ wọn lọ́dọ̀ ẹnì kan bí kò ṣe lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa mi, tí ó bá jẹ́ pé ẹ bá fura"
  26,114,Èmi kò sì níí lé àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo dànù
  26,115,Èmi kò sì jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe olùkìlọ̀ pọ́nńbélé.”
  26,116,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Dájúdájú tí ìwọ Nūh kò bá jáwọ́ (nibí ìpèpè rẹ) dájúdájú o máa wà nínú àwọn tí a máa jù lókò.”"
  26,117,"Ó sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, dájúdájú àwọn ènìyàn mi ti pè mí ní òpùrọ́"
  26,118,"Nítorí náà, ṣèdájọ́ tààrà láààrin èmi àti àwọn. Kí o sì la èmi àti àwọn t’ó wà pẹ̀lú mi nínú àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo.”"
  26,119,A la òun àti àwọn t’ó wà pẹ̀lú rẹ̀ nínú ọkọ̀ ojú-omi t’ó kún kẹ́kẹ́
  26,120,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A tẹ àwọn t’ó ṣẹ́kù rì sínú omi"
  26,121,Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn. Ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò sì jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo
  26,122,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Òun mà ni Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"
  26,123,Àwọn ìran ‘Ād pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́
  26,124,"Nígbà tí arákùnrin wọn, (Ànábì) Hūd, sọ pé: “Ṣé ẹ ò níí bẹ̀rù (Allāhu) ni"
  26,125,Dájúdájú èmi ni Òjíṣẹ́ olùfọkàntán fun yín
  26,126,"Nítorí náà, ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu, kí ẹ sì tẹ̀lé mi"
  26,127,Èmi kò sì bèèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan ní ọwọ́ yín lórí rẹ̀. Kò sí ẹ̀san mi lọ́dọ̀ ẹnì kan àfi lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá
  26,128,Ṣé ẹ óò máa kọ́ ilé ńlá ńlá sí àwọn àyè gíga (kí ẹ lè) máa fi àwọn olùrékọjá ṣẹ̀fẹ̀
  26,129,Ẹ sì ń kọ́ àwọn ilé ńlá ńlá bí ẹni pé ẹ máa ṣe gbére (nílé ayé yìí)
  26,130,"Nígbà tí ẹ bá sì gbá (ènìyàn mú láti fìyà jẹ wọ́n), ẹ̀ ń gbá wọn mú ní ìgbámú aláìlójú-àánú"
  26,131,"Nítorí náà, ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu, kí ẹ sì tẹ̀lé mi"
  26,132,Ẹ bẹ̀rù Ẹni tí Ó ràn yín lọ́wọ́ pẹ̀lú ohun tí ẹ mọ̀
  26,133,Ó ràn yín lọ́wọ́ pẹ̀lú àwọn ẹran-ọ̀sìn àti àwọn ọmọ
  26,134,àti àwọn ọgbà oko pẹ̀lú àwọn ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú omi
  26,135,Dájúdájú èmi ń páyà ìyà ọjọ́ ńlá fun yín.”
  26,136,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Bákan náà ni fún wa; yálà o kìlọ̀ fún wa tàbí o ò sí nínú àwọn olùkìlọ̀"
  26,137,Èyí kò jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe ìwà àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́
  26,138,Wọn kò sì níí jẹ wá níyà.”
  26,139,"Nítorí náà, wọ́n pè é ní òpùrọ́. A sì pa wọ́n run. Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn. Ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò sì jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  26,140,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Òun mà ni Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"
  26,141,Àwọn ìran Thamūd pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́
  26,142,"Nígbà tí arákùnrin wọn, (Ànábì) Sọ̄lih, sọ pé: “Ṣé ẹ ò níí bẹ̀rù (Allāhu) ni"
  26,143,Dájúdájú emi ni Òjíṣẹ́ olùfọkàntán fun yín
  26,144,"Nítorí náà, ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu, kí ẹ sì tẹ̀lé mi"
  26,145,Èmi kò sì bèèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan ní ọwọ́ yín lórí rẹ̀. Kò sí ẹ̀san mi lọ́dọ̀ ẹnì kan àfi lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá
  26,146,"Ṣé kí wọ́n fi yín sílẹ̀ síbi n̄ǹkan tí ó wà (nílé ayé) níbí yìí (nínú ìgbádùn ayé, kí ẹ jẹ́) olùfọkànbalẹ̀"
  26,147,nínú àwọn ọgbà oko àti ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú omi
  26,148,àti oko irúgbìn pẹ̀lú igi dàbínù tí ọ̀gọ́mọ̀ rẹ̀ tutù
  26,149,Ẹ sì ń gbẹ́ àwọn ilé sínú àwọn àpáta (gẹ́gẹ́ bí) akọ́ṣẹ́-mọṣẹ́
  26,150,"Nítorí náà, ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu, kí ẹ sì tẹ̀lé mi"
  26,151,Kí ẹ sì má ṣe tẹ̀lé àṣẹ àwọn aláṣejù
  26,152,"àwọn t’ó ń ṣèbàjẹ́ lórí ilẹ̀, tí wọn kò sì ṣe rere.”"
  26,153,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ìwọ kúkú wà nínú àwọn eléèdì"
  26,154,"Ìwọ kò sì jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe abara bí irú wa. Nítorí náà, mú àmì kan wá tí o bá wà nínú àwọn olódodo.”"
  26,155,"Ó sọ pé: “Èyí ni abo ràkúnmí kan. Omi wà fún òhun, omi sì wà fún ẹ̀yin náà ní ọjọ́ tí a ti mọ̀"
  26,156,Ẹ má ṣe fi aburú kan kàn án nítorí kí ìyà ọjọ́ ńlá má baà jẹ yín.”
  26,157,"Wọ́n sì gún un pa. Nítorí náà, wọ́n sì di alábàámọ̀"
  26,158,Ìyà náà jẹ wọ́n. Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn. Ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò sì jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo
  26,159,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Òun mà ni Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"
  26,160,Ìjọ Lūt pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́
  26,161,"Nígbà tí arákùnrin wọn, (Ànábì) Lūt, sọ pé: “Ṣé ẹ ò níí bẹ̀rù (Allāhu) ni"
  26,162,Dájúdájú èmi ni Òjíṣẹ́ olùfọkàntán fun yín
  26,163,"Nítorí náà, ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu, kí ẹ sì tẹ̀lé mi"
  26,164,Èmi kò sì bèèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan ní ọwọ́ yín lórí rẹ̀. Kò sí ẹ̀san mi lọ́dọ̀ ẹnì kan àfi lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá
  26,165,Ṣé àwọn ọkùnrin nínú ẹ̀dá ni ẹ̀yin ọkùnrin yóò lọ máa bá (fún adùn ìbálòpọ̀)
  26,166,"Ẹ sì ń pa ohun tí Olúwa yín dá fun yín tì nínú àwọn ìyàwó yín! Àní sẹ́, ìjọ alákọyọ ni ẹ̀yin.”"
  26,167,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Tí ìwọ Lūt kò bá jáwọ́ (nibí ìpèpè rẹ) dájúdájú o máa wà nínú àwọn tí a máa lé jáde kúrò nínú ìlú.”"
  26,168,"Ó sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú èmi wà nínú àwọn olùbínú sí iṣẹ́ (aburú) ọwọ́ yín"
  26,169,"Olúwa mi, la èmi àti àwọn ènìyàn mi níbí ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́ (aburú)"
  26,170,"Nítorí náà, A la òun àti àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ pátápátá"
  26,171,Àfi arúgbóbìnrin kan tí ó wà nínú àwọn t’ó ṣẹ́ kù lẹ́yìn (láààrin àwọn tí A parẹ́)
  26,172,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A pa àwọn yòókù run"
  26,173,A rọ òjò lé wọn lórí tààrà. Òjò àwọn tí A kìlọ̀ fún sì burú
  26,174,Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn. Ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò sì jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo
  26,175,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Òun mà ni Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"
  26,176,Àwọn ará ’Aekah pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́
  26,177,"Nígbà tí arákùnrin wọn, (Ànábì) Ṣu‘aeb, sọ pé: “Ṣé ẹ̀yin kò níí bẹ̀rù (Allāhu) ni"
  26,178,Dájúdájú èmi ni Òjíṣẹ́ olùfọkàntán fun yín
  26,179,"Nítorí náà, ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu, kí ẹ sì tẹ̀lé mi"
  26,180,Èmi kò sì bèèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan ní ọwọ́ yín lórí rẹ̀. Kò sí ẹ̀san mi lọ́dọ̀ ẹnì kan àfi lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá